Package: gwasglue
Title: GWAS Summary Data Sources Connected to Analytical Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gibran", "Hemani", , "g.hemani@bristol.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0920-1055")),
    person("Tom", "Palmer", , "remlapmot@hotmail.com", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4655-4511"))
  )
Description: Many tools exist that use GWAS summary data for
    colocalisation, fine mapping, Mendelian randomization, visualisation,
    etc. This package is a conduit that connects R packages that can
    retrieve GWAS summary data to various tools for analysing those data.
    This package is part of the MRC Integrative Epidemiology Unit OpenGWAS
    system.
